{"tid":1704481,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"各位香港人，希望大家入黎睇一睇","createTime":"2019-11-10T16:56:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T17:07:42.000Z","uid":275679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"98847b4ecb1b911ab16ba71fb6f85956724a34d1","tid":1704481,"uid":275679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T16:56:13.000Z","msg":"由6月至今，黑警已經毫無底線踐踏我地每一個人尊嚴同生活自由，大家唔好再諗住無打死人無強姦，唔好再呃自己仲喺度日日返工，睇完新聞嬲兩嬲就算。<br />\n周梓樂手足已經喺活生生比黑警害死，今日再有人喺又一城頂層俾黑警打到無反應，生死仲未知。<br />\n<br />\n好希望大家真喺要齊反抗，為我地6月至今失去手足執仇。只要大家踏出自己心理關口，每次行動齊心我地先可以真正做到<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港</span></span>。千祈唔好睇少自己，謹記住<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">多你一個真喺多好多</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港，時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"e77b1ce1badb51cd342edd917b983766f7bd5d5c","tid":1704481,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T17:07:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">搭巴士有落千其要記得撳鐘<br />\n唔撳鐘巴士司機係唔會埋站㗎</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">另外駕駛人士請注意</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1DJ0kNC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1DJ0kNC.png&h=09b514a8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9AHPYzi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9AHPYzi.jpg&h=91dc0471&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}